balance	raw text	information	doc	17	18	31	32	The reserve base The reserve base of an institution is defined in relation to elements of its balance sheet, and each credit institution subject to minimum reserve requirements uses the statistical information collected under Regulation ECB/2008/32 to calculate its reserve base and to verify the fulfilment of its reserve requirement over the maintenance period (Article 11).																																		
